      <lg xml:id="TolE0107">
<l>uyiriṟu coṉmu ṉuyirvaru vaḻiyu</l>
<l>muyiriṟu coṉmuṉ meyvaru vaḻiyu</l>
<l>meyyiṟu coṉmu ṉuyirvaru vaḻiyu</l>
<l>meyyiṟu coṉmuṉ meyvaru vaḻiyumeṉ</l>
<l>ṟivveṉa vaṟiyak kiḷakkuṅ kālai</l>
<l>niṟutta collē kuṟittuvaru kiḷaviyeṉ</l>
<l>ṟāyī riyal puṇarnilaic cuṭṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The final vocalized consonant</l>
<l>is of the same nature as the final vowel.</l>
      </lg>
